:: Refuse to Sell User Data {"position":"1425,925","size":"100,100"}
### Game Over

"I can't do it", you say. "This violates every principle of user trust we claim to stand for."

The room goes cold. Your manager looks at the CEO, then back at you.

''Manager:'' "How disapointing.... We hired you because we thought you'd do as you're told. Not act as the company's moral compass. If you won't do the work we'll find someone who will".


